<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta name="layout" content="main">
    <title>About - Gr8Ladies</title>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

    <div class="row">
        <div class="box">
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <hr>

                <h2 class="intro-text text-center">About
                    <strong>Gr8Ladies</strong>
                </h2>
                <hr>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-2">
                <asset:image class="img-responsive img-border-left" src="gr8ladies.png" alt="Gr8Ladies Logo"/>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-10">
                <p>Gr8Ladies is an organization for the support of women in the Gr8 (Groovy, Grails, Gradle, Griffon, etc) community.  Although our mission is to bring
                more women into the Gr8 community, our events are always open to anyone of any gender!  We could never achieve our mission without allies.  We strive to create a warm
                welcoming environment for individuals at every stage of their programming careers.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="box">
            <div class="col-lg-10 col-lg-offset-1">
                <h2 class="text-center">We host a variety of events including:</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><p>Technical Talks</p></li>
                    <li><p>Educational Workshops for beginners and experienced developers new to Groovy (<g:link
                            uri="workshops">Gr8Workshops</g:link>)</p></li>
                    <li><p>Conference Meetups</p></li>
                    <li><p>Social Events</p></li>
                    <li><p>Women in tech functions with other local groups</p></li>
                </ul></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="box">
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <hr>

                <h2 class="intro-text text-center"><strong>Leadership Team</strong>
                </h2>
                <hr>
            </div>

            <div class="col-sm-2"></div>

            <div class="col-sm-4 text-center">
                <asset:image class="img-responsive" src="jenn.jpg" alt="Jenn"/>

                <h3>Jenn Strater
                    <small>Co-Founder</small>
                </h3>
            </div>

            <div class="col-sm-4 text-center">
                <img class="img-responsive" src="http://placehold.it/450" alt="Allison">

                <h3>Allison
                    <small>Co-Founder</small>
                </h3>
            </div>

            <div class="col-sm-2"></div>

            <div class="clearfix"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="box">
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <hr>

                <h2 class="intro-text text-center"><strong>Volunteers</strong></h2>
                <hr>
            </div>

            <div class="col-sm-12">
                <div class="col-sm-4 text-center col-sm-offset-4">
                    <img class="img-responsive" src="http://placehold.it/300?text=YOUR%20NAME%20HERE">
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-sm-12">
                <p class="text-center">To volunteer with Gr8Ladies, email <a href="mailto:volunteers@gr8ladies.org">volunteers@gr8ladies.org</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

</div>
<!-- /.container -->
</body>

</html>
